<h2>&quot;Arts et Savoirs&quot; (Zeitschriftenheft)</h2>
<h3>&quot;Herbert Spencer en France : mise au jour d’une influence&quot; (dir. Niklas Bender)</h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='2444'></abbr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
